Here: http://php.net/manual/en/mongoclient.construct.php
It states the connection timeout setting is:
{quote}
"connectTimeoutMS"

How long a connection can take to be opened before timing out in milliseconds.
{quote}

The value says its suppose to be milliseconds but actually it works as seconds.

I wanted to connection to timeout after 1 second so I wrote
{code}
$options = ["connectTimeoutMS" => 1000] ;
$this->connection = new MongoClient($this->connection_string, $options);
{code}
The result was the code waited very long. 

To get it to work I had to do this:
{code}
$options = ["connectTimeoutMS" => 1] ;
$this->connection = new MongoClient($this->connection_string, $options);
{code}
